sar2png.pl Changelog
====================

Version: 1.2.0 - 18.10.2017
---------------------------

+ Added custom color support (Colors are defined at the beginning of the script).
+ Added -w for a SWAP graph.
+ Will now always output a 24hrs graph, Fixes the graph resetting at 00:00.

Version: 1.1.1 - 15.11.2011
---------------------------

+ The chart legend now shows average values

Version: 1.1 - 14.11.2011
-------------------------

+ Added support for network statistics (this feature is only supported at GNU/Linux)
+ Added default parameter 'precision' (The number of numerals after the decimal pointprecision (set to 1))

Version: 1.0 - 22.09.2010
-------------------------

+ First release
